Interface Feature

All Known Subinterfaces:
BEDFeature
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicFeature, FullBEDFeature, GeliTextFeature, OldDbSNPFeature, SimpleBEDFeature, VariantContext
public interface Feature

Represents a locus on a reference sequence. The coordinate conventions for start and end are implementation dependent, no specific contact is specified here.
